# NSApplication.DelegateReply.success

**Case**

Indicates the operation succeeded.

## Declaration

```swift
case success
```

## Constants

- **NSApplication.DelegateReply.cancel**: Indicates the user cancelled the operation.
- **NSApplication.DelegateReply.failure**: Indicates an error occurred processing the operation.
